Javanese keyboard
This extension provides a Javanese script keyboard layout in Chrome OS. How to enable: after installing the extension, head over to chrome://settings/languages then add Indonesian (ID). If the option does not show up, sign out once and retry the procedure. Switch keyboard layouts with Alt+Shift until you hit the Javanese keyboard (symbol: ID*).
